snippet.title: Minigame Madness - FINALLY on Steam! Wishlist Now!
snippet.description:
Wishlist now! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1408080/Minigame_Madness?utm_source=YouTube&utm_campaign=NewTrailer

Our Steam store page is FINALLY live! 😁 If you like what you see, please go add the game to your Steam wishlist. Thanks so much everyone! ♥️

Twitter - https://twitter.com/ChaoticDevs
Discord - https://discord.com/invite/BajtRQc
Website - https://MinigameMadness.net

Chaotic Entertainment is currently working on Minigame Madness, a frantic online multiplayer party game for up to 16 players. Compete with friends or strangers in a huge ever-growing collection of fun and unique free-for-all minigames to earn awesome outfits and gadgets!

Wishlist now! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1408080?utm_source=YouTube&utm_campaign=NewTrailer

Minigame Madness New Trailer
